     1→# index.hbs
     3→`index.hbs` is the handlebars template that is used to render the book. The
     4→markdown files are processed to html and then injected in that template.
     5→
     6→If you want to change the layout or style of your book, chances are that you
     7→will have to modify this template a little bit. Here is what you need to know.
