theme/syntax-highlighting.md
     1→# Syntax highlighting
     3→mdBook uses [Highlight.js](https://highlightjs.org) with a custom theme
     4→for syntax highlighting.
     5→
     6→Automatic language detection has been turned off, so you will probably want to
     7→specify the programming language you use like this:
     8→
     9→~~~markdown
    10→```rust
    11→fn main() {
    12→    // Some code
    13→}
    14→```
    15→~~~
    16→
